title: ⚽🔥 Top Betting Picks – World Cup Qualifiers 2026 Edition
content_md:
We're back with smart betting insights for this Sunday's World Cup Qualifiers action 📊🎯💰

1️⃣ Georgia 🇬🇪 vs Bulgaria 🇧🇬
Georgia had a solid performance against Turkey and needs the win to stay in the race.
✅ Pick: Georgia to WIN 🏆🇬🇪

2️⃣ Turkey 🇹🇷 vs Spain 🇪🇸
A tough clash! Turkey will try to surprise but without taking big risks. Expect goals.
✅ Pick: Over 2 Goals ⚽📈

3️⃣ Germany 🇩🇪 vs Northern Ireland 🇮🇪
Germany is under pressure to bounce back after a disappointing last match.
✅ Pick: Germany to WIN 🏆🇩🇪

4️⃣ Poland 🇵🇱 vs Finland 🇫🇮
A tight and low-scoring game, but Poland should edge it.
✅ Pick: Poland to WIN & Under 2 Goals ⚽🔒
